T1  - Insider Trading Restrictions and Informed Trading in Peer Stocks
AU  - Deuskar, Prachi
AU  - Khatri, Aditi
AU  - Sunder, Jayanthi
Y1  - 2024/06/05
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2025/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.02907
