TY  - JOUR
T1  - Resolving Tensions Between Heterogeneous Investors in a Startup
AU  - Chen, Shiqi
AU  - Lambrecht, Bart M.
Y1  - 2024/06/13
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2025/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.01724
