T1  - Vaccine Progress, Stock Prices, and the Value of Ending the Pandemic
AU  - Acharya, Viral V.
AU  - Johnson, Timothy
AU  - Sundaresan, Suresh
AU  - Zheng, Steven
Y1  - 2024/06/19
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2025/03/01
